languages.text: "...укрытые в Паутине души... жажду... отдай их мне... ищи знаки... возможности... разбивай запреты... уничтожай барьеры... найди удушитель и разрушь его... дай Истине вновь проникнуть в Темный город... помогу тебе..."

languages.text: "...sheltered in the Web of Souls... thirsting... give them to me... look for the signs... opportunities... break down inhibitions... destroy barriers... find the stifler and destroy it... let the Truth permeate the Dark City once more... help you..."

languages.text: “……潜藏在灵魂之网中……渴求着……把它们带给我……寻找迹象……机会……突破抑制……摧毁障碍……找到扼杀一切之人……消灭它……让真理再次渗透到黑暗之城……帮助你……”
languages.original_text: "...sheltered in the Web of Souls... thirsting... give them to me... look for the signs... opportunities... break down inhibitions... destroy barriers... find the stifler and destroy it... let the Truth permeate the Dark City once more... help you..."

traits.locale_text: “……潜藏在灵魂之网中……渴求着……把它们带给我……寻找迹象……机会……突破抑制……摧毁障碍……找到扼杀一切之人……消灭它……让真理再次渗透到黑暗之城……帮助你……”

languages.text: 「…魂の網に守られ…渇き…捧げたまえ…兆しを見よ…機会を…抑制を打ち破り…障壁を破壊し…窒息の元凶を破り…再び仄暗き都に真実を伝えよ…お前を救う…」
languages.original_text: "...sheltered in the Web of Souls... thirsting... give them to me... look for the signs... opportunities... break down inhibitions... destroy barriers... find the stifler and destroy it... let the Truth permeate the Dark City once more... help you..."

languages.text: «... refugiados en la Red de Almas... sedientos... entrégamelos... busca las señales... oportunidades... quiebra las inhibiciones... destruye las barreras... encuentra al reprimidor y acaba con él... deja que la Verdad vuelva a impregnar la Ciudad Siniestra... ayudaré...».
